dcterms:creator: R. Carmona
M. Lauri`ere
dcterms:description: A graphon representing a constant interaction strength among players, leading to a mean-field game where all players are symmetric and interact equally.
dcterms:title: Constant Graphon

dcterms:creator: M. Anthropelos
T. Geng
T. Zariphopoulou
dcterms:description: A graphon that divides players into two independent populations, each with its own interaction strength, reflecting competition among different groups.
dcterms:title: Two-block Graphon

dcterms:creator: A. Aurell
R. Carmona
G. Dayanıklı
M. Lauri`ere
dcterms:description: A graphon that models a star-like interaction structure where one major player interacts with all others, while the other players do not interact among themselves.
dcterms:title: Star Graphon

dcterms:creator: A. Aurell
R. Carmona
M. Lauriere
dcterms:description: A graphon that models interactions where the strength of interaction is stronger when players are closer to each other, reflecting a min-max structure.
dcterms:title: Min-max Graphon

dcterms:creator: E. Bayraktar
R. Wu
X. Zhang
dcterms:description: A graphon that follows a power-law distribution, where interaction strength increases as players' indices approach one.
dcterms:title: Power-law Graphon
